prompts.frontCover: A minimalist and charming cartoon greeting card design. On a clean, solid off-white background, two cute, simple cartoon figures of girlfriends are depicted in a flat 2D style. The figure on the left is holding a single, long-stemmed daisy and is playfully trying to tickle the chin of the figure on the right with the flower. The figure on the right is laughing, leaning back slightly with her eyes crinkled in a joyful expression. Both figures are drawn with simple lines and shapes, wearing casual, simple outfits like t-shirts and pants. Centered above them, in a beautiful, elegant, and readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao". The overall composition is clean, balanced, and filled with lighthearted, sweet humor.
